Class OperatingSystemPattern

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.uadetector.internal.data.domain.OperatingSystemPattern
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<OperatingSystemPattern>, Identifiable, OrderedPattern<OperatingSystemPattern>
@Immutable
public final class OperatingSystemPattern
extends Object
implements Identifiable, OrderedPattern<OperatingSystemPattern>, Serializable

The OperatingSystemPattern class represents the detection information for a specific operating system item.

A OperatingSystemPattern object is immutable, their values cannot be changed after creation.
